e and highly reliable SMPA. Numerical results validate the\nstability and resilience of H2DF coding in SMPA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Jan 2019 08:06:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-23"}
