ess viscous heating can\ntrigger thermal ionization in the disk innermost region to self-sustain\nmagnetorotational instability turbulence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Jan 2019 13:17:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Feb 2019 04:46:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-01"}
